<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Isu Neih Hinna Nuom</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu neih hinna nuom,
 Kipahna thuguk chu;
 Ka thagau muonna ei pie'i,
 Isu neih chauh kipahna.

[V2]
 Isu neih chitna bulpi,
 Isu neih hauhna bukim;
 Isu neih chu vannuoi tawh kikhenna.

[V3]
 2. Isu neih hinna nuom,
 Mihau hawn neizo lo;
 Miching hawn a hethiem puou,
 Kuo zieka dangchak ahim?

[V4]
 3. Van Kanaan ka In ding,
 Khawvel ka khuolzinna;
 Aigupta a hak taluo'i,
 Ka Lal Isu ei puiin.

[V5]
 4. Ken Isu kanei hi,
 Genviel leng vannuoi ah;
 Taksanna'n ka muchien tai,
 A thihna mel Kross bul ah.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>261</hymn_number>
</song>